">─</span><span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#851165;\">主题式沟通。</span></span>\r\n						</p>\r\n						<p>\r\n							<span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#851165;font-size:10pt;\">※</span><span style=\"line-height:18px;font-family:Verdana;color:#464646;font-size:9pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#851165;font-size:10pt;\">学员互相演练沟通化解自己内在对往生亲人的牵挂与伤痛及学员心得分享。</span><span style=\"line-height:18px;font-family:Verdana;color:#464646;font-size:9pt;\"><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#851165;font-size:10pt;\">※</span><span style=\"line-height:18px;font-family:Verdana;color:#464646;font-size:9pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#851165;font-size:10pt;\">本单元沟通目的：</span>\r\n						</p>\r\n						<p>\r\n							<span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:Arial;color:#851165;font-size:10pt;\">1.</span><span style=\"line-height:18px;font-family:Verdana;color:#464646;font-size:9pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#851165;font-size:10pt;\">破除迷信思想，重塑对灵魂观念的正确认知。</span><span style=\"line-height:18px;font-family:Verdana;color:#464646;font-size:9pt;\"><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:Arial;color:#851165;font-size:10pt;\">2.</span><span style=\"line-height:18px;font-family:Verdana;color:#464646;font-size:9pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#851165;font-size:10pt;\">学会正确面对死亡</span>\r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n				</tr>\r\n				<tr>\r\n					<td valign=\"center\" width=\"150\" style=\"border:1px solid #DDDDDD;font-family:Verdana, 宋体, sans-serif;background-color:#FEE8FF;\">\r\n						<p>\r\n							<span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:Arial;color:#851165;font-size:10pt;\">PM17:30-18:30</span>\r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n					<td valign=\"center\" width=\"337\" style=\"border:1px solid #DDDDDD;font-family:Verdana, 宋体, sans-serif;background-color:#FEE8FF;\">\r\n						<p>\r\n							<span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:Arial;color:#851165;font-size:10pt;\">60</span><span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#851165;font-size:10pt;\">分鐘－晚餐用餐及休息時間</span>\r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n				</tr>\r\n				<tr>\r\n					<td valign=\"center\" width=\"150\" style=\"border:1px solid #DDDDDD;font-family:Verdana, 宋体, sans-serif;\">\r\n						<p>\r\n							<span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:Arial;color:#851165;font-size:16px;\">AM18:30~PM:21:30</span>\r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n					<td valign=\"center\" width=\"337\" style=\"border:1px solid #DDDDDD;font-family:Verdana, 宋体, sans-serif;\">\r\n						<p>\r\n							<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#851165;\">◎</span><span style=\"line-height:18px;font-family:Verdana;color:#464646;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#851165;\">带课讲师自选单元</span></span>\r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n				</tr>\r\n			</tbody>\r\n		</table>\r\n		<p style=\"color:#444444;font-size:14px;text-align:center;font-family:simsun;background-color:#F3F8FB;\">\r\n			<br />\r\n		</p>\r\n		<p style=\"color:#444444;font-size:14px;font-family:simsun;background-color:#F3F8FB;\">\r\n			<br />\r\n		</p>\r\n		<p style=\"color:#444444;font-size:14px;font-family:simsun;background-color:#F3F8FB;\">\r\n			<br />\r\n		</p>\r\n		<p style=\"color:#444444;font-size:14px;font-family:simsun;background-color:#FDFEFF;\">\r\n			<strong><span style=\"line-height:22px;font-family:楷体_GB2312;color:#ED1C24;font-size:11.5pt;\">第四天</span></strong>\r\n		</p>\r\n		<p style=\"color:#444444;font-size:14px;font-family:simsun;background-color:#FDFEFF;\">\r\n			<br />\r\n		</p>\r\n		<table width=\"668\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 10px;padding:0px;width:668px;\">\r\n			<tbody>\r\n				<tr>\r\n					<td valign=\"center\" width=\"143\" style=\"border:1px solid #DDDDDD;font-family:Verdana, 宋体, sans-serif;background-color:#990066;\">\r\n						<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n							<span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#FFFFFF;font-size:10pt;font-weight:bold;\">時間</span>\r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n					<td valign=\"center\" width=\"344\" style=\"border:1px solid #DDDDDD;font-family:Verdana, 宋体, sans-serif;background-color:#990066;\">\r\n						<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n							<span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#FFFFFF;font-size:10pt;font-weight:bold;\">內容</span>\r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n				</tr>\r\n				<tr>\r\n					<td valign=\"center\" width=\"143\" style=\"border:1px solid #DDDDDD;font-family:Verdana, 宋体, sans-serif;\">\r\n						<p>\r\n							<span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:Arial;color:#851165;font-size:10pt;\">AM9:00~AM10:20</span>\r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n					<td valign=\"center\" width=\"344\" style=\"border:1px solid #DDDDDD;font-family:Verdana, 宋体, sans-serif;\">\r\n						<p>\r\n							<span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#7030A0;font-size:16px;\">◎心识科学之时光旅行</span>\r\n						</p>\r\n						<p>\r\n							<span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;color:#6F3198;\">※“时间”之研究与探讨：时间为何是“非线性”的存在，为什么过去、现在、未來同时并存！如何证明时间是一体的现象。</span><span style=\"line-height:18px;font-family:Verdana;color:#464646;font-size:9pt;\"><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#7030A0;font-size:10pt;\">※时间会因速度的不同而有所改变吗？时间会因为重力的不同而有所改变吗？时间会因为空间的不同而有所改变吗？</span>\r\n						</p>\r\n						<p>\r\n							<span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;color:#6F3198;\">※时间可以被压缩的范例探讨；由科学观点来解释各种不同时间状态并说明“时间”的成因为何。</span>\r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n				</tr>\r\n				<tr>\r\n					<td valign=\"center\" width=\"143\" style=\"border:1px solid #DDDDDD;font-family:Verdana, 宋体, sans-serif;background-color:#FEE8FF;\">\r\n						<p>\r\n							<span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:Arial;color:#851165;font-size:10pt;\">AM10:20~AM10:30</span>\r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n					<td valign=\"center\" width=\"344\" style=\"border:1px solid #DDDDDD;font-family:Verdana, 宋体, sans-serif;background-color:#FEE8FF;\">\r\n						<p>\r\n							<span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#851165;font-size:10pt;\">下课中场休息</span><span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:Arial;color:#851165;font-size:10pt;\">10</span><span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#851165;font-size:10pt;\">分钟</span>\r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n				</tr>\r\n				<tr>\r\n					<td valign=\"center\" width=\"143\" style=\"border:1px solid #DDDDDD;font-family:Verdana, 宋体, sans-serif;\">\r\n						<p>\r\n							<span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:Arial;color:#851165;font-size:10pt;\">AM10:30~PM:12:00</span>\r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n					<td valign=\"center\" width=\"344\" style=\"border:1px solid #DDDDDD;font-family:Verdana, 宋体, sans-serif;\">\r\n						<p>\r\n							<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#851165;\">◎</span><span style=\"line-height:18px;font-family:Verdana;color:#464646;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#851165;\">传统文化中佛学对时间的阐述</span></span>\r\n						</p>\r\n						<p>\r\n							<span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#851165;font-size:10pt;\">※从佛学经典中来了解时间存在的现象。</span><span style=\"line-height:18px;font-family:Verdana;color:#464646;font-size:9pt;\"><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#851165;font-size:10pt;\">※</span><span style=\"line-height:18px;font-family:Verdana;color:#464646;font-size:9pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#851165;font-size:10pt;\">引用经典来说明「时间」存在的原理。何谓超</span><span style=\"line-height:18px;font-family:Verdana;color:#464646;font-size:9pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#851165;font-size:10pt;\">越三界？物质界、空间界、时间界，需要如何超越之研究说明。</span>\r\n						</p>\r\n						<p>\r\n							<span style=\"line-height:18px;font-family:Verdana;color:#464646;font-size:9pt;\"></span>\r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n				</tr>\r\n				<tr>\r\n					<td valign=\"center\" width=\"143\" style=\"border:1px solid #DDDDDD;font-family:Verdana, 宋体, sans-serif;background-color:#FEE8FF;\">\r\n						<p>\r\n							<span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:Arial;color:#851165;font-size:10pt;\">PM12:00~PM13:30</span>\r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n					<td valign=\"center\" width=\"344\" style=\"border:1px solid #DDDDDD;font-family:Verdana, 宋体, sans-serif;background-color:#FEE8FF;\">\r\n						<p>\r\n							<span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:Arial;color:#851165;font-size:10pt;\">90</span><span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#851165;font-size:10pt;\">分钟－午餐用餐及休息时间</span>\r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n				</tr>\r\n				<tr>\r\n					<td valign=\"center\" width=\"143\" style=\"border:1px solid #DDDDDD;font-family:Verdana, 宋体, sans-serif;\">\r\n						<p>\r\n							<span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:Arial;color:#851165;font-size:10pt;\">PM13:30~PM14:20</span>\r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n					<td valign=\"center\" width=\"344\" style=\"border:1px solid #DDDDDD;font-family:Verdana, 宋体, sans-serif;\">\r\n						<p>\r\n							<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#851165;\">◎</span><span style=\"line-height:18px;font-family:Verdana;color:#464646;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#851165;\">辩证地看到“过去世”的心理意象及开发内在潜能的探讨</span></span>\r\n						</p>\r\n						<p>\r\n							<span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#851165;font-size:10pt;\">※</span><span style=\"line-height:18px;font-family:Verdana;color:#464646;font-size:9pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#851165;font-size:10pt;\">运用沟通回溯“过去世”来解决当下生活中的困惑与疾病困扰。</span><span style=\"line-height:18px;font-family:Verdana;color:#464646;font-size:9pt;\"><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#851165;font-size:10pt;\">※</span><span style=\"line-height:18px;font-family:Verdana;color:#464646;font-size:9pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#851165;font-size:10pt;\">开发内在潜能之沟通步骤说明：如何利用潜意识投射出的“过去世”中的内容来开发与提升内在潜能。</span>\r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n				</tr>\r\n				<tr>\r\n					<td valign=\"center\" width=\"143\" style=\"border:1px solid #DDDDDD;font-family:Verdana, 宋体, sans-serif;background-color:#FEE8FF;\">\r\n						<p>\r\n							<span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:Arial;color:#851165;font-size:10pt;\">PM14:20-15:00</span>\r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n					<td valign=\"center\" width=\"344\" style=\"border:1px solid #DDDDDD;font-family:Verdana, 宋体, sans-serif;background-color:#FEE8FF;\">\r\n						<p>\r\n							<span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#851165;font-size:10pt;\">下午茶时间</span>\r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n				</tr>\r\n				<tr>\r\n					<td valign=\"center\" width=\"143\" style=\"border:1px solid #DDDDDD;font-family:Verdana, 宋体, sans-serif;\">\r\n						<p>\r\n							<span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:Arial;color:#851165;font-size:10pt;\">PM15:00~PM17:30</span>\r\n						</p>\r\n						<p>\r\n							<span style=\"line-height:18px;font-family:Verdana;color:#464646;font-size:9pt;\"></span>\r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n					<td valign=\"center\" width=\"344\" style=\"border:1px solid #DDDDDD;font-family:Verdana, 宋体, sans-serif;\">\r\n						<p>\r\n							<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#851165;\">◎</span><span style=\"line-height:18px;font-family:Verdana;color:#464646;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#851165;\">深层沟通演练</span><span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:Arial;color:#851165;\">─</span><span style=\"line-height:18px;font-family:Verdana;color:#464646;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#851165;\">主题式沟通</span></span>\r\n						</p>\r\n						<p>\r\n							<span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#851165;font-size:10pt;\">※</span><span