pan style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#851165;font-size:10pt;\">儿童心灵探讨。为何父母是孩子最大的伤害来源，父母是如何伤害孩子而不自知的？</span>\r\n						</p>\r\n						<p>\r\n							<span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#851165;font-size:10pt;\">※</span><span style=\"line-height:18px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#851165;font-size:10pt;\">胎儿心灵问题探讨，胎教深层影响是什么？</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#851165;font-size:10pt;\">※</span><span style=\"line-height:18px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#851165;font-size:10pt;\">如何解读孩子身体的疾病现象，孩子透过疾病想告诉父母什么讯息？</span>\r\n						</p>\r\n						<p>\r\n							<span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#851165;font-size:10pt;\">※如何与孩子沟通，了解孩子的想法，倾听孩子的心声。</span>\r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n				</tr>\r\n				<tr>\r\n					<td width=\"150\" style=\"border:#ECE9D8;font-family:Verdana, 宋体, sans-serif;vertical-align:top;background-color:#FEE8FF;\">\r\n						<p>\r\n							<span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:Arial;color:#851165;font-size:10pt;\">AM10:20~AM10:30</span>\r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n					<td width=\"337\" style=\"border:#ECE9D8;font-family:Verdana, 宋体, sans-serif;vertical-align:top;background-color:#FEE8FF;\">\r\n						<p>\r\n							<span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#851165;font-size:10pt;\">下课中场休息</span><span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:Arial;color:#851165;font-size:10pt;\">10</span><span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#851165;font-size:10pt;\">分钟</span>\r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n				</tr>\r\n				<tr>\r\n					<td width=\"150\" style=\"border:#ECE9D8;font-family:Verdana, 宋体, sans-serif;vertical-align:top;background-color:transparent;\">\r\n						<p>\r\n							<br />\r\n						</p>\r\n						<p>\r\n							<br />\r\n						</p>\r\n						<p>\r\n							<span style=\"line-height:19px;font-family:Arial;color:#851165;font-size:10pt;\">AM10:40~PM:12:00</span>\r\n						</p>\r\n					</td