ze:14px;font-family:宋体;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;text-align:justify;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;text-align:center;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;text-align:center;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<img class=\"\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/UCpvbJoePCnZYeOLRzSal67u4Ugj5OrquZgibsh73iasvcWjCUicUbV1MaeEpu0avWafGxZqIbvrXETS4j0rhCjkg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1\" style=\"height:auto !important;width:auto !important;\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<img class=\"\" width=\"auto\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/nAYdtUHuP7qIEqYYKtSK6dnxOzu85Sm3JdKAH9sm8sVOlIhtcnU6lQXSeEib9ZrjNjWCugmHpzGsZcicEBia8kJ7g/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1\" style=\"height:auto !important;width:auto !important;\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">【唯识深层沟通蔚然中心】</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">【</span>1<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">】</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">解决内心的困惑及工作生活中问题。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">【</span>2<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">】健康、家庭教育、财富、事业、情感等方面出现了问题。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">【</span>3<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">】在生活工作，遇到困惑，不知道如何处理！</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">【</span>4<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">】小孩经常让你操心操劳，不知道如何教育！</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">【</span>5<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">】财富无法显化出来，不知道如何显化。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">【</span>6<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">】夫妻之间，感情不和，或者反感，怨恨，不知道如何处理。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;text-indent:28px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">扫描关注蔚然中心平台，心灵成长美文，参与更多公益课程，感兴趣的朋友回复，邀请您进入公益分享群学习，还有更多一对一个案沟通，让您获得清明圆满幸福的人生！</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">电话：</span><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\">0531 ——58969006</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">微信：萧蔚：</span><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\">13805311479</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，蔚然然：</span><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica, sans-serif;\">weiran58969006</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background:white;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:楷体;\">奥体中路与康虹路交叉口向东 新生活家园北区73号楼2单元302室。电话：0531-58969006</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background:white;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-family:楷体;\">了解更多敬请登录：www. Jnwrzx.com</span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;text-indent:28px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">深层沟通愿景</span>:\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;text-indent:28px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">愿迷惑者得以清明</span>!\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;text-indent:28px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">愿痛苦者得以安康</span>!\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;text-indent:28px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">愿贫困者得以丰盛</span>!\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;text-indent:28px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">愿安息者得以解脱</span>!\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;text-indent:28px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">愿我们的生命得以完整</span>!\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;text-indent:28px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>','','','','',160,'N','N','','',0,0,'N',0,0,'Y',0,'','Y',1505291057),(51,1,'','','父母必修课｜4月14日-4月15日《如何培育全像式思维的孩子》如期而至','','','','','','','',1,0,'','','','','','<h2 class=\"rich_media_title\" id=\"activity-name\" style=\"font-weight:400;font-size:24px;font-family:&quot;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n		《如何培养全像式思维的孩子》\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n		如果您已经为人父母长辈，如果您是教育工作者，如果您想改善亲子关系，或者您想突破自己的惯性思维，掌握自己的命运，如果您想了解全像式思维。那么《如何培养全像式思维的孩子》是您最佳的选择。\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n		我的孩子怎么了？孩子越大，和自己的关系越远，越不能理解孩子到底想什么，甚至对立叛逆？\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n		为了孩子的前途费劲心思，结果却不尽人意，教育好孩子的关键在哪里？\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n		孩子的行为真的让我很担心：不愿沟通、爱享受、不愿努力、不能坚持、逃学、早恋、迷上电脑、游戏<span>....</span>怎么办？\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n		真的都是孩子的问题吗？我们真的了解孩子吗？孩子的思维模式和我们到底有什么不用？怎样了解和帮助他们？\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n		有一种思维模式叫全像式思维，拥有它，你可以真正走进孩子的心，它让你跳脱个人的思维局限，真正地理解孩子内在的需要，由此找到你和孩子间最适合的相处。拥有它，你能轻而易举地协助孩子顺利成长为一名健康快乐的成功人士！\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n		<span>&nbsp;</span>时间：<span>4</span>月<span>14--15</span>日<span>&nbsp; 9:00-17</span>：<span>00</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n		<span>&nbsp;</span>地点：济南高新区新生活家园南区<span>23-1</span>（蔚然心灵教育）\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n		<span>&nbsp;</span>参加对象：学员，非学员\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n		<span>&nbsp;</span>指导老师<span>: </span>郁云老师\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:5.25pt;\">\r\n		报名费用<span>: 980/</span>人\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n		<span>&nbsp;</span>报名热线：<span>0531-85969006</span>\r\n	</p>\r\n<br />\r\n</h2>','','','','',1041,'N','N','','',0,0,'N',0,0,'Y',0,'','Y',1523347363);
